<p> <small> <font color="red">
           Music is a collection of coordinated sound. Music concerned
           with combining vocal or instrumental sounds for beauty of form or 
           emotional expression, usually according to cultural standards 
           of rhythm, melody. Music is an art form, and cultural activity, 
           whose medium is sound. Music is nothing but sounds civilized into time and tune.
           Music is the universal language of mankind. 
</font> </small> </p>

<h2> <b> <font color="purple"> Etymology </font> </b> </h2>
<p> <big> <font color="blue">
         The word, 'music' is derived from Greek word μουσική (mousike; "art of the Muses").
</font> </big> </p>

<h2> <b> <font color="purple"> History </font> </b> </h2>
<p> <big> <font color="blue">
         Prehistoric music have been founded in the different archaeological sites.
         A look at the Old Testament in the Bible reveals the people 
         were devoted to the practice of music.
         The medieval era (476 to 1400), which took place during the Middle Ages, 
         started with the introduction of monophonic chanting.
         Musical notation was used since Ancient times in Greek culture, but in the Middle Ages,
         notation was first introduced by the Catholic church.
         In the 20th-century, music prevailed via the invention of new electric technologies.
         The focus of art music in the 20th century was characterized by exploration of new rhythms,
         styles, and sounds. Jazz became an important genre of music over the course of the 20th century,
         and during the second half of that century, rock music did the same.
         In the 1990s, an increasingly large range of computerized hardware musical devices 
         and instruments and software were used. 
         In the 2020s, soft synths and computer music apps make it possible for bedroom producers 
         to create and record some types of music.
</font> </big> </p>

      <fieldset> <font color="blue"> 
      <legend> Name: </legend>

      <label> First name: </label> <br>
      <input type="text" id="fname" name="fname"> <br>    
      <label> Last name: </label> <br>
      <input type="text" id="lname" name="lname"> <br> </font>
      </fieldset>
 
      <fieldset> <font color="blue">
      <legend> Gender: </legend>
      
      <input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="male">
      <label> Male </label> <br>      
      <input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="female">
      <label> Female </label> <br>      
      <input type="radio" id="other" name="gender" value="other">
      <label> Other </label> <br> </font>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset> <font color="blue">
      <legend> Date Of Birth: </legend>
      
      <label> Day: </label> <br>
      <input type="number" id="day" name="day"> <br>
      <label> Month: </label> <br>
      <input type="number" id="month" name="month"> <br>
      <label> Year: </label> <br>
      <input type="number" id="year" name="year"> <br> </font>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset> <font color="blue">
      <legend> Choice of Instrument: </legend>

      <label> Select your choice of Instrument: </label> <br>
      <input list="insrtuments" name="insrtuments">
      <datalist id="insrtuments">
      <option value="Violin">
      <option value="Guitar">
      <option value="Piano">
      <option value="Drums">
      <option value="Vocals">
      </datalist> </font>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset> <font color="blue">
      <legend> Pick Days for Classes: </legend>
 
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Monday </label> <br>      
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Tuesday </label> <br>      
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Wednesday </label> <br>      
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Thursday </label> <br>      
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Friday </label> <br>      
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Saturday </label> <br>      
      <input type="checkbox" id="day" name="day">
      <label> Sunday </label> <br> </font>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset> <font color="blue">
      <legend> Comments: </legend>
      <textarea name="message" rows="10" cols="30">
      </textarea> </font>
      </fieldset>

      <fieldset> <font color="blue">
      <legend> Contact Details: </legend>

      <label> E-mail: </label> <br>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email"> <br>
      <label> Mobile Number: </label> <br>
      <input type="number" id="mnumber" name="mnumber"> <br>
      <label> Address: </label> <br>
      <input type="text" id="address" name="address"> <br> </font>
      </fieldset>

      <font color="blue"> <input type="submit" value="Submit"> </font>
      
      </form>
